rosas.lou.calculator
Interface Calculator

All Known Implementing Classes:
RPNFractionCalculator
public interface Calculator

An Interface by Lou Rosas. This is the interface to be used by all Versions of Calculators (Fraction or Decimal, RPN or Algebriac notation) that can be conceived. Thus, it is declared an interface because all known types of calculators MUST implement these four basic operations described here.
